revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== From {{der|en|ceb|yakal}}. ===Noun=== {{en-noun|~}} # {{lb|en|Philippines}} {{taxlink|Shorea astylosa|species|ver=180325}}; a tree [[endemic]] to the [[Philippines]]. # The wood from this tree. ===Anagrams=== * {{anagrams|en|a=aakly|Kayla}} [[Category:en:Malvales order plants]] [[Category:en:Woods]] ---- ==Cebuano== ===Pronunciation=== * {{hyphenation|ceb|ya|kal}} ===Noun=== {{head|ceb|noun}} # {{l|en|yakal}} ({{taxlink|Shorea astylosa|species|ver=180325}}) # the wood from this tree [[Category:ceb:Malvales order plants]] [[Category:ceb:Trees]] [[Category:ceb:Woods]] ---- ==Masbatenyo== ===Noun=== {{head|msb|noun|head=yakál}} # {{l|en|yakal}} ({{taxlink|Shorea astylosa|species|ver=180707}}) ---- ==Tagalog== ===Noun=== {{tl-noun|yakál}} # {{l|en|yakal}} ({{taxlink|Shorea astylosa|species|ver=180707}}) # The [[hardwood]] or [[lumber]] from this tree. {{C|tl|Malvales order plants|Trees|Woods}} ---- ==Waray-Waray== ===Noun=== {{head|war|noun|head=yakál}} # a [[kind]] of [[timber]] [[tree]] ({{taxlink|Hopea plagata|species|ver=180325}}) {{rfv-sense|war}} # [[hardwood]] or [[lumber]] from Hopea plagata
